title: Ohio State Players Say No Warning Signs Preceeded Teammate's Death
teaser: The Ohio State football team is baffled by the disappearance and apparent suicide of Kosta Karageorge, who was found dead inside a dumpster Sunday. Friends described him as positive, goofy and lighthearted.
